de.rwth.i2.attestor.graph.morphism.checkers

Class AbstractVF2MorphismChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth.i2.attestor.graph.morphism.checkers.AbstractVF2MorphismChecker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MorphismChecker
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    VF2EmbeddingChecker, VF2IsomorphismChecker, VF2MinDepthEmbeddingChecker

    public abstract class AbstractVF2MorphismChecker
extends Object
implements MorphismChecker
    An abstract class providing a default implementation of MorphismChecker to find graph morphisms mapping a pattern graph into a target graph. Subclasses of AbstractVF2MorphismChecker usually determine the actual algorithm that is applied to find morphisms. The class supports to check whether at least one morphism exists and to iteratively get all existing morphisms.
    Author:
    Christoph
